name: TequilaDictionary
0: ”Alexa, ask Tequila Dictionary what distillery has the nom 1445”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tequila dictionary
des: Using this Alexa skill, you can get the name of a tequila distillery by specifying the four digit nom number. Nom numbers can be found printed on every bottle of tequila.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
